law.history: Repealed 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 105, sec. 34, effective July 15, 2002. -- Created 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 427, sec. 6, effective July 14, 2000.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Conversion of prepaid dental plans to single service organization or health discount plan -- Reissuance of certificate of authority -- Net worth and risk-based capital requirements.
